<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na hun su-thiengtho in, Lalpa pawl zingin,
 Amah ah um zingin, A Thu'n kivak in;
 Pathien chate pawlin hatlo panpih in,
 A vangsakna na hung chan theihna dingin.

[V2]
 2. Na hun su-thiengtho in, khawvel a bei zel,
 Na hun pha cheng chengte Isu di'n mangin;
 Amah na bat theihna'n Isu en zingin,
 Amah tawbang na hih na guolte'n mun au.

[V3]
 3. Na hun su-thiengtho in na Puipa, hi hen,
 Bang hungtung mahlele taih mangsan ta kin;
 Lungkham leh nawp laiin na Lalpa zuiin,
 Isu lam en zingin, A thu ging detin.

[V4]
 4. Na hun su-thiengtho in, lungnem in umin,
 Na lungthim ngaihtuoh na A thu'n nun sakin;
 Thagau in hehpihna luiah hunpui in,
 Chunglam vanah A na chuh sem thei tan la.</lyrics>
<title>TAKE TIME TO BE HOLY</title>
<hymn_number>358</hymn_number>
</song>